Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:02.85,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Equipe médica, na frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:04.50,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.34,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Chopper, deixe esses caras te ajudarem!
